{{CorrectTitle|title=u'Tal'ac Range}}
The '''u'Tal'ac Range''' was a mountain range at [[Upper Bal'ta'ran Cluster]], in [[Guiteica/Legends|Guiteica]].<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

Slave [[Aul Tarrus Vishav]] was imprisoned there before his intended execution, but he escaped, killing his guards and becoming a legend among the slaves of Bal'ta'ran mines.<ref name="AIR" />

